               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18630713-name-392" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18630713-name-392" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18630713-name-392" type="surname" value="HAUFF"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18630713-name-392" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>CHARLES HAUFF</persName>
                  </hi>. I live at 38, Queen-street, Cheapside—on 12th June, I was looking in a shop window in Cheapside—I felt something break at my watch—I found it was gone from my waistcoat pocket, and the chain was hanging down—I looked round and saw two men, whom I took hold of—one was the prisoner, the other escaped—I charged the prisoner with stealing my watch—he said, "You have made a mistake"—a Mr. Van Steight was also there—he said, "Here is the watch"—the bow was broken—I got the watch back.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18630713-name-393" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18630713-name-393" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18630713-name-393" type="surname" value="STEIGHT"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18630713-name-393" type="given" value="LEWIS VAN"></interp>LEWIS VAN STEIGHT</persName>
                  </hi>. I live at No. 6, Cambridge-terrace, Islington—on the evening of 12th June, I was in Cheapside—I saw the prisoner there, and heard Mr. Hauff say to him, "You have stolen my watch"—he took hold of the prisoner, and the other escaped—I saw the watch in the prisoner's hand, and felt him put it into my pocket—I turned round quick, took hold of it, and said to Mr. Hauff, "Here is the watch."</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="186307130074"></xptr>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I am not guilty of stealing it. I am guilty of taking it from the man that stole it.</p>
